      <title>津巴布韦央行考虑采取更多措施保护货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/zimbabwe-central-bank-mulls-more-measures-to-protect-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦央行行长约翰·穆沙亚万胡 (John Mushayavanhu) 表示，他将考虑动用该国储备来保护以黄金为支撑的货币免受严重的市场混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/zimbabwe-central-bank-mulls-more-measures-to-protect-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 09:37:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
