      <title>美联储大幅降息即将获得验证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/fed-s-favored-price-gauge-seen-substantiating-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储青睐的价格指标和消费者需求概况被认为证实了央行大幅降息的举措以及主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对经济依然强劲的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/fed-s-favored-price-gauge-seen-substantiating-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《信贷周刊》：美联储大幅降息加剧估值焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/valuation-angst-is-being-stoked-by-fed-s-big-cut-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者纷纷将资金投入公司债券，风险溢价不断收紧，美联储降息再次点燃了人们对美国避免经济衰退的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/valuation-angst-is-being-stoked-by-fed-s-big-cut-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预算之争迫在眉睫，马克龙任命新法国政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/macron-appoints-antoine-armand-as-france-s-new-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命安托万·阿尔芒为财政部长，将这位 33 岁、政治经验有限的人推入一场紧迫的预算之争，他必须获得极右翼的默许支持，以避免政府垮台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/macron-appoints-antoine-armand-as-france-s-new-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 17:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克屈服并遵守巴西的法律命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/x-names-representative-to-comply-with-ruling-cnn-brasil-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克作出了让步，决定遵守巴西的法庭命令，试图结束长达数月的冲突，这场冲突最终导致数百万美元的罚款以及他的社交网络 X 在拉丁美洲最大经济体被禁止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/x-names-representative-to-comply-with-ruling-cnn-brasil-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 00:58:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
